title: Low FPS
body: I was running at a stunning 25 fps but now I am running at 4 fps! I updated the video card, defragged, reduced windows settings to performance. I have no Idea what to do next!

The troubleshooting you've done so far is solid, but there are other factors as well that could be causing fps problems.  Outdated drivers is a big factor in that!  Go over our [FPS issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting) guide to make sure everything gets running smoothly.  That should fix up your fps!
